<p>First I check pom xmls but could not find the exact point to disable this maven-checkstyle-plugin. I don’t know which super clever engineer enable this in examples and have not tried it under windows. But this kind of errors actually make people to stop learning java. The java language is easy but this environmental problems very frustrating.</p>

<p>So really easy way to disable this problem is giving -Dcheckstyle.skip=true  as an argument in mvn command like this</p>

<p>mvn clean compile exec:java -Dcheckstyle.skip=true</p>

